track_notes: Nice hike on the Mountains to Sea Trail from the Craggy Gardens picnic area
This is the track described in the notes created by KW4JM which is to enter the MST trail at Potato Field Gap which shortens the hike quite a bit compared to the KI4SVM Track

This is the long way to Lane Pinnacle but if you are up for a hike when the Parkway is closed this will get you there via the MST from Bull Gap.  The trail passes by the remains of Rattlesnake Lodge and has some interesting remains of rock work from the lodge plus a historical marker.  Dean ~ K2JB
